GNU Toolchains for ARM processors
=================================

Supported platforms
-------------------

  * V2i routers (ARM 926EJ-S)
  * V3 routers (ARM Cortex-A8)
  * V4 routers (ARM Cortex-A72)
  * V4i routers (ARM Cortex-A53)

Requirements
------------

  * 64-bit Linux distribution
  * 1 GB of free space in /opt

Install instructions
--------------------

  ```
  dpkg -i deb/*.deb
  ```

  or

  ```
  rpm -i rpm/*.rpm
  ```

Directory structure
-------------------

```
  Toolchains
   |
   |--deb                       DEB packages
   |   |
   |   |--gcc-icr-v2i-armv5-*   GNU Toolchain for ARM 926EJ-S processors
   |   |--gcc-icr-v3-armv7-*    GNU Toolchain for ARM Cortex-A8 processors
   |   |--gcc-icr-v4-aarch64-*  GNU Toolchain for ARM Cortex-A72 processors
   |   +--gcc-icr-v4i-aarch64-* GNU Toolchain for ARM Cortex-A53 processors
   |
   |--rpm                       RPM packages
   |   |
   |   |--gcc-icr-v2i-armv5-*   GNU Toolchain for ARM 926EJ-S processors
   |   |--gcc-icr-v3-armv7-*    GNU Toolchain for ARM Cortex-A8 processors
   |   |--gcc-icr-v4-aarch64-*  GNU Toolchain for ARM Cortex-A72 processors
   |   +--gcc-icr-v4i-aarch64-* GNU Toolchain for ARM Cortex-A53 processors
   |
   |--COPYING                   GNU General Public License version 2
   |--COPYING.LIB               GNU Lesser General Public License version 2.1
   |--COPYING.RUNTIME           GCC Runtime Library Exception version 3.1
   |--COPYING3                  GNU General Public License version 3
   |--COPYING3.LIB              GNU Lesser General Public License version 3
   +--README                    This file
```

